  "detailed_description": "<h1>CHECK OUT OTHER GAMES</h1><p><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829850/extras/0584c6052f42e420e54c028a163e124d.avif?t=1768609493\" width=1560 height=336 /></span>This game was entirely made on RPG Maker MV and it suffers from a native engine problem: the frame rate drop. We optimized the game as much as we could and we're still working on new improvements. If you experience a frame rate drop, we suggest saving the game and restarting it.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Steam Achievements are disabled</strong> until we find a solution for this frame rate problem. We hope understand the situation and thank you for your support.</i>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829850/extras/01fa4a329bc0c30c121d2ad582fe14f1.avif?t=1768609493\" width=1560 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829850/extras/e1644c5342658144897af8d2a8db5bbc.webp?t=1768609493\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Date system with 14 unique characters; </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829850/extras/e1644c5342658144897af8d2a8db5bbc.webp?t=1768609493\" width=17 height=18 /></span>More than 20 unique endings;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829850/extras/e1644c5342658144897af8d2a8db5bbc.webp?t=1768609493\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Character creation with class and magical element customization;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829850/extras/fc5c0b9abb70e6014a2e4f707c5be850.poster.avif?t=1768609493\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829850/extras/fc5c0b9abb70e6014a2e4f707c5be850.webm?t=1768609493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829850/extras/fc5c0b9abb70e6014a2e4f707c5be850.mp4?t=1768609493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829850/extras/e1644c5342658144897af8d2a8db5bbc.webp?t=1768609493\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Characters with unique classes and skills; </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829850/extras/e1644c5342658144897af8d2a8db5bbc.webp?t=1768609493\" width=17 height=18 /></span>More than 90 characters to join your team;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829850/extras/e1644c5342658144897af8d2a8db5bbc.webp?t=1768609493\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Classic Mode for advanced players and Story Mode for those who want to focus on the narrative;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829850/extras/9220fb03aa67e78196a04bcebd8e21b5.poster.avif?t=1768609493\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829850/extras/9220fb03aa67e78196a04bcebd8e21b5.webm?t=1768609493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829850/extras/9220fb03aa67e78196a04bcebd8e21b5.mp4?t=1768609493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829850/extras/e1644c5342658144897af8d2a8db5bbc.webp?t=1768609493\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Skill improvements based on the level of relationship with the characters;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829850/extras/e1644c5342658144897af8d2a8db5bbc.webp?t=1768609493\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Random battles with different formations real-time created; </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829850/extras/e1644c5342658144897af8d2a8db5bbc.webp?t=1768609493\" width=17 height=18 /></span>More than 30 hours of gameplay;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829850/extras/e1644c5342658144897af8d2a8db5bbc.webp?t=1768609493\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Unique Maps;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829850/extras/69947bfe380fc617b78dd8cb92172e26.avif?t=1768609493\" width=1560 height=80 /></span> The continent of Libertas faces a threat: the Empire of Aeterna. Military and powerful, each day it annihilates the nearby kingdoms, destroying their cultures and taking over them. One by one, the kingdoms fell until the ones who weren't dominated decided to group themselves and fight back under the banner of the Libertasians Alliance. Angered by the group's attitude, the great Emperor Eligius Emeritus IV now seeks to find the 6 magic crystals created by the Goddess Vitalia to control the terrible serpent Obitus and force the entire world to bow down to him. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829850/extras/686523b0b185dd24b268b977cdb06282.avif?t=1768609493\" width=616 height=467 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829850/extras/8fa24b8b651c8c93abb06a93e8842661.avif?t=1768609493\" width=1560 height=80 /></span>Harem, Otome, Boys Love, Yaoi, Bara, Gay, Lesbian, Transgender, Amare, Dating Sims, B+B, G+G, B+G</p>",
